description:
AutoProvisioning:  Records of automatic provisioning events for RAN cells, including timestamp, location, cell identifiers, data type, format version, and provisioning status.

dateTime: Timestamp of the provisioning event.
Area_Name: Name of the area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely redundant).
vsDataType: Type of provisioning data.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
AutoProvisioning.rbsConfigLevel:  Level of RBS configuration achieved by auto-provisioning.
AutoProvisioning.autoProvisioningId: Unique identifier for this auto-provisioning instance.
